reef heron
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:<i>Egretta sacra sacra</i>, also called <i> blue heron </i>, occas, <i> blue reef heron </i>(see b. and c. below). See also (blue) crane, matuku-moana. [AND <i> Egretta sacra </i> of coastal mainland Austr. and elsewhere 1848.]

